Reclusa::

She smiled and walked outside, towards the direction that Perceptor
had indicated.  She had a regal air about her, since she thought of
herself as almost royalty since she was decedant from a high arachnid
background.  Her form moved and swayed in one fluid motion as she
walked.  
"So, who is it exactly that you'll be introducing me to? And what are
thier ranks?" Keeping her tone of voice as if she was speaking to a
bot of equal statis, though she didn't think any bot could be.
